  ./COVERAGE.md:987:| `org.jetbrains.kotlin:kotlin-scripting-jvm` | [2.3.21](metadata/org.jetbrains.kotlin/kotlin-scripting-jvm/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> Kotlin Scripting JVM provides JVM-specific APIs and utilities for configuring, compiling, evaluating, caching, and running Kotlin scripts. It supplies JVM classpath, classloader, dependency, and REPL support used by Kotlin scripting hosts on the JVM.</details> | [100.0% (39/39 calls)](stats/org.jetbrains.kotlin/kotlin-scripting-jvm/) |
